       du Stravinski le Lundi de Pâques 22 Avril.
       Suisse
       Hi, I’m Martina and I’ve been building costumes for 3 years. I love
       the angled and clean low-poly aesthetics of early 3D computer
       graphics and want to bring them to life with my costumes. Anubis is
       my third cosplay. The first armor I built, Master Chief, was
       completely made of paper. I like experimenting with different
       materials and learning new techniques for every build.
